### Get all notes (default pagination)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/notes
Accept: application/json

### Get notes with custom limit
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/notes?limit=20
Accept: application/json

### Get notes with custom offset and limit
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/notes?limit=10&offset=20
Accept: application/json

### Get notes with large limit (capped at 100)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/notes?limit=200
Accept: application/json
